text: President Biden has created more jobs in his first 7 months than any POTUS in history.
The Biden administration has created more than double the number of jobs per month, on average, than any other administration going back to George H.W. Bush.
A viral Facebook post shared over 7,400 times claims Democratic presidential nominee Joe Biden said he would create 550 million new jobs during an Oct. 2 speech.
Trump lost as many jobs as Biden gained during his first five months
